OL,7,FReeves told broadcasters on Wednesday:
OL,8,F"We looked in full at the ombudsman
OL,9,Frecommendations and they said that
OL,10,Faround 90% of women did know that
OL,11,Fthese changes were coming.
OL,13,F"And as Chancellor, I have to account
OL,14,Ffor every penny of taxpayers' money
OL,15,Fspent.
