OL,4,Cwouldn't be the 'best use of
OL,5,Ctaxpayers' money'
OL,7,FThe watchdog said in March that the
OL,8,Fwomen should be paid up to #2,950
OL,9,Feach, a package with a potential total
OL,10,Fcost of #10.5 billion to the public
OL,11,Fpurse, as poor communication meant
OL,12,Fthey had lost out on the change to
OL,13,Fplan their retirement finances.
OL,15,FKendall however accepted a finding of
OL,16,Fmaladministration and apologised for
OL,17,Fthere being a 28-month delay in
OL,18,Fwriting to 1950s-born women.
