OL,7,FKendall, Sir Keir Starmer, and Cabinet
OL,8,FOffice minister Pat McFadden are among
OL,9,Fthe other Labour frontbenchers who
OL,10,Fpreviously appeared in photographs
OL,11,Falongside Waspi women to lend their
OL,12,Fsupport to the group.
OL,14,FThe ombudsman has criticised the
OL,15,Fgovernment's decision not to
OL,16,Fcompensate the women.
