OL,3,CReeves says Waspi compensation
OL,4,Cwouldn't be the 'best use of
OL,5,Ctaxpayers' money'
OL,7,FRebecca Hilsenrath, the ombudsman,
OL,8,Ftold Times Radio: "It's great that the
OL,9,FGovernment are saying that our
OL,10,Fintervention will lead to service
OL,11,Fimprovements and it's fair to say also
OL,12,Fthat people who come to us,
OL,13,Foverwhelmingly, are motivated by
OL,14,Fwanting things to improve for other
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,F"But what we don't expect is for an
OL,18,Facknowledgement to be made by a public
OL,19,Fbody that it's got it wrong but then
OL,20,Frefuse to make it right for those
OL,21,Faffected."
