OL,7,FWhen Labour was led by Jeremy Corbyn,
OL,8,Fit promised some form of compensation
OL,9,Ffor the Waspi women in both its 2017
OL,10,Fand 2019 manifestos.
OL,12,FBut the party did not make this pledge
OL,13,Fduring this year's general election.
OL,15,FThe Conservatives hit out at the
OL,16,F"betrayal" of Waspi women by Labour,
OL,17,Fbut shadow business secretary Andrew
OL,18,FGriffith acknowledged the Tories might
OL,19,Fnot have offered any compensation
OL,20,Feither.
